extends pug/layout.pug

block head
  title Leverage the power of locize for every team role | locize
  link(rel="canonical", href="/for-your-team.html")
  

block headDescription
  meta(name='description', content='Project managers, translators, and developers should read this. Use locize to your advantage in every team job.')

block content
  
  section.section-white
    .container
      .row
        .col-lg-12.text-center
          .section-heading
            h2 locize - brings your team together
            p.head For project managers, translators and developers.
            p.text-muted Leverage the power of locize for every team role.
            hr


  section.section-primary.features.text-center
    .container
      .row
        .col-lg-12.text-center
          .section-heading
            h2 For Project / Translation Managers
            p.head
              | Being supportive - while tracking performance.
            hr
      .row
        .col-md-12
          .container-fluid
            .row
              .col-md-6
                .feature-item
                  .device-wrapper(style="margin: 40px auto 0;")
                    .device(data-device="MacbookPro", data-orientation="portrait", data-color="black", style="z-index: 0;")
                      .screen
                        img.img-responsive(src='img/screenshots/screen/dashboard_s.jpg', alt='locize dashboard', loading='lazy')
              .col-md-6
                .feature-item
                  h3 Keep the overview
                  p Track project progress from your dashboard. All your projects including versions in one place.
                  p Drill down to get more information about each individual project, language, file.
                  p Never miss an untranslated segment again independent the numbers of projects you have to lead.
                    
          
          .container-fluid
            .row
              .col-md-6
                .feature-item
                  h3 Powerful statistics
                  p Get insights for different metrics like modifications done, number of words per language, downloads done, special metrics for developers, etc.
                  p See how your project and success grow over time.
              .col-md-6
                .feature-item
                  .device-wrapper(style="margin: 0 auto 0;")
                    .device(data-device="MacbookPro", data-orientation="portrait", data-color="black", style="z-index: 0;")
                      .screen
                        img.img-responsive(src='img/screenshots/screen/stats_s.jpg', alt='locize statistics', loading='lazy')
                    

      .row
        .col-md-12
          .container-fluid
            .row
              .col-md-6
                .feature-item
                  .device-wrapper(style="margin: 0 auto 0;")
                    .device(data-device="MacbookPro", data-orientation="portrait", data-color="black", style="z-index: 0;")
                      .screen
                        img.img-responsive(src='img/screenshots/screen/history_s.jpg', alt='locize history', loading='lazy')
              .col-md-6
                .feature-item
                  h3 History
                  p Who, when? We can't tell you why but at least who did a change to your translations.
                  p Be able to reply to those questions.
                    
          
          .container-fluid
            .row
              .col-md-6
                .feature-item
                  h3 Order translations
                  p While you can let your translation done by freelancers or inhouse employees using locize itself you also got the options to directly order translations from inside locize.
                  p Currently you can order directly from localistars, TextMaster or BLEND.
              .col-md-6
                .feature-item
                  .device-wrapper(style="margin: 0 auto 0;")
                    .device(data-device="MacbookPro", data-orientation="portrait", data-color="black", style="z-index: 0;")
                      .screen
                        img.img-responsive(src='img/screenshots/screen/ordering_s.jpg', alt='locize ordering', loading='lazy')


      .row
        .col-md-12
          .container-fluid
            .row
              .col-md-6
                .feature-item
                  .device-wrapper(style="margin: 0 auto 0;")
                    .device(data-device="MacbookPro", data-orientation="portrait", data-color="black", style="z-index: 0;")
                      .screen
                        img.img-responsive(src='img/screenshots/screen/slack_s.jpg', alt='locize notification', loading='lazy')
              .col-md-6
                .feature-item
                  h3 Keep your team up to date
                  p Keep your team up to date by enabling our notification integration with slack.
                  p Get notified when something noteworthy happens to your localization project.
                    
          
